label: ISTPc
text:
and you see something like this... 
Little marks on a tree,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity131
label: ISTPc
text: maybe you pay attention, maybe you don't.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity132
label: ISTPc
text:
You go another 50 metres 
and you see this...

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity133
label: ISTPc
text: You should be paying attention.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity134
label: ISTPc
text:
Another 50 metres, if you haven't been 
paying attention, you see this...

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity135
label: ISTPc
text:
And at this point,
you're paying attention.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity136
label: ISTPc
text:
And you've just learned that this...
is important,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity137
label: ISTPc
text:
it's relevant 
because it means this,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity138
label: ISTPc
text:
and anything that is related, 
any information related to your survival

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity139
label: ISTPc
text:
is stuff that you're going to pay
attention to

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity140
label: ISTPc
text:
and therefore you're going
to remember it.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity141
label: ISTPc
text: If it's related to your personal goals,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity142
label: ISTPc
text: then you're going to pay attention to it.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity143
label: ISTPc
text:
If it's relevant, 
you're going to remember it.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity144
label: ISTPc
text:
So, the first rule, 
first principle for learning a language

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity145
label: ISTPc
text:
is focus on language content 
that is relevant to you.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity146
label: ISTPc
text: Which brings us to tools.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity147
label: ISTPc
text:
We master tools by using tools 
and we learn tools the fastest

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity148
label: ISTPc
text: when they are relevant to us.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity149
label: ISTPc
text: So let me share a story.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity150
label: ISTPc
text: A keyboard is a tool.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity151
label: ISTPc
text:
Typing Chinese a certain way, 
there are methods for this. That's a tool.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity152
label: ISTPc
text: I had a colleague many years ago

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity153
label: ISTPc
text:
who went to night school; 
Tuesday night, Thursday night,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity154
label: ISTPc
text: two hours each time, practicing at home,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity155
label: ISTPc
text:
she spent nine months, 
and she did not learn to type Chinese.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity156
label: ISTPc
text: And one night we had a crisis.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity157
label: ISTPc
text:
We had 48 hours to deliver 
a training manual in Chinese.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity158
label: ISTPc
text:
And she got the job, 
and I can guarantee you

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity159
label: ISTPc
text: in 48 hours, she learned to type Chinese

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity160
label: ISTPc
text:
because it was relevant,
it was meaningful, it was important,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity161
label: ISTPc
text: she was using a tool to create value.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity162
label: ISTPc
text:
So the second principle for learning 
a language is to use your language

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity163
label: ISTPc
text:
as a tool to communicate 
right from day one.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity164
label: ISTPc
text: As a kid does.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity165
label: ISTPc
text:
When I first arrived in China, 
I didn't speak a word of Chinese,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity166
label: ISTPc
text:
and on my second week, 
I got to take a train ride overnight.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity167
label: ISTPc
text:
I spent eight hours sitting 
in the dining car

label: ISTPc
text: talking to one of the guards on the train,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity169
label: ISTPc
text: he took an interest in me for some reason,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity170
label: ISTPc
text: and we just chatted all night in Chinese

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity171
label: ISTPc
text:
and he was drawing pictures and 
making movements with his hands

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity172
label: ISTPc
text:
and facial expressions 
and piece by piece by piece

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity173
label: ISTPc
text: I understood more and more.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity174
label: ISTPc
text:
But what was really cool, 
was two weeks later,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity175
label: ISTPc
text:
when people were talking Chinese 
around me,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity176
label: ISTPc
text: I was understanding some of this

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity177
label: ISTPc
text:
and I hadn't even made any effort 
to learn that.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity178
label: ISTPc
text:
What had happened, 
I'd absorbed it that night on the train,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity179
label: ISTPc
text: which brings us to the third principle.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity180
label: ISTPc
text: When you first understand the message,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity181
label: ISTPc
text:
then you will acquire 
the language unconsciously.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity182
label: ISTPc
text:
And this is really, 
really well documented now,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity183
label: ISTPc
text:
it's something called 
comprehensible input.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity184
label: ISTPc
text:
There's 20 or 30 years 
of research on this,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity185
label: ISTPc
text: Stephen Krashen, a leader in the field,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity186
label: ISTPc
text:
has published all sorts of 
these different studies

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity187
label: ISTPc

label: ISTPc
text:
The purple bars show the scores

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity189
label: ISTPc
text:
The purple people were people who had 
learned by grammar and formal study,

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity190
label: ISTPc
text:
the green ones are the ones 
who learned by comprehensible input.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity191
label: ISTPc
text:
So, comprehension works. 
Comprehension is key

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity192
label: ISTPc
text:
and language learning is not about 
accumulating lots of knowledge.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity193
label: ISTPc
text:
In many, many ways 
it's about physiological training.

id: ISTPc_How to learn any language in six months | Chris Lonsdale | TEDxLingnanUniversity194
label: ISTPc
text:

did great in English at school,

text: she got A grades all the way through,

label: ISTPc
text:
went through college, A grades, 
went to the US

label: ISTPc
text:
and found she couldn't understand

text:
And people started asking her:

in our brain that filter in

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt0
label: ENFPc
text:
Translator: Vn Thy
Reviewer: Yu Xie

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt1
label: ENFPc
text:
We are having the wrong conversation
about our comfort zone.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt2
label: ENFPc
text:
The phrase "getting out
of your comfort zone"

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt3
label: ENFPc
text:
is thrown around so much today
online and in motivational quotes

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt4
label: ENFPc
text: that it's begun to lose its meaning.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt5
label: ENFPc
text:
And this is because
we don't clearly understand

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt6
label: ENFPc
text: what our comfort zone is,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt7
label: ENFPc
text: and it seems counterintuitive to leave it

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt8
label: ENFPc
text: because it's where we feel the most safe.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt9
label: ENFPc
text:
It also sounds like
we're sugar-coating something

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt10
label: ENFPc
text: that we don't want to talk about,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt11
label: ENFPc
text: which is fear.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt12
label: ENFPc
text:
Let me tell you a bit more about my story
and how fear has played a role in it.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt13
label: ENFPc
text: I come from a family of travelers.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt14
label: ENFPc
text:
My mom started a travel agency
when she was younger than I am now,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt15
label: ENFPc
text:
and growing up they never left me behind
when they went on their adventures.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt16
label: ENFPc
text:
I graduated early and got a degree
from community college

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt17
label: ENFPc
text: by the time I turned 18.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt18
label: ENFPc
text:
And at that time I had traveled
to around 70 countries.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt19
label: ENFPc
text: This was the point in my life

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt20
label: ENFPc
text: where people began to ask me

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt21
label: ENFPc
text:
the most intimidating question
that you can ask a young person:

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt22
label: ENFPc
text: "What are you going to do next?"

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt23
label: ENFPc
text: And in attempt to answer that question,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt24
label: ENFPc
text:
I began by asking myself
what I was most passionate about,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt25
label: ENFPc
text: which has always been travelling,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt26
label: ENFPc
text:
and how to make the most
out of the cards that I was dealt,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt27
label: ENFPc
text:
which was how much
travel experience I've had at my age.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt28
label: ENFPc
text: That's when it dawned on me.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt29
label: ENFPc
text:
I had over six years
to break the world record

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt30
label: ENFPc
text:
for the youngest person
to travel to every country.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt31
label: ENFPc
text:
And this was the perfect opportunity
that I was looking for

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt32
label: ENFPc
text:
to get out of the books
and into the real world.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt33
label: ENFPc
text:
In retrospect, I had no idea
what I was getting myself into.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt34
label: ENFPc
text:
Flash-forward two and a half years later,
and I spent countless hours

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt35
label: ENFPc
text:
crammed on planes, trains,
chicken buses, tuk-tuks and junk boats

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt36
label: ENFPc
text: travelling with nothing but a backpack.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt37
label: ENFPc
text:
I have encountered health issues,
spanning from malaria in West Africa

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt38
label: ENFPc
text:
to hospital-worthy
food poisoning in Pakistan.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt39
label: ENFPc
text:
I learned how to cope with
public anxiety attacks

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt40
label: ENFPc
text: by myself in foreign countries,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt41
label: ENFPc
text:
and I endured the brain-sizzling
frustration of dealing with bureaucrats

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt42
label: ENFPc
text: from every country that requires a visa.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt43
label: ENFPc
text:
Believe it or not, these have been
some of my most treasured memories

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt44
label: ENFPc
text:
because they were the most
defining moments of my life,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt45
label: ENFPc
text: spent far, far away from my comfort zone.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt46
label: ENFPc
text:
Proving to Guiness World Records
that I have traveled to every country

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt47
label: ENFPc
text: was a completely different story.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt48
label: ENFPc
text:
According to a very strict
pack of guidelines,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt49
label: ENFPc
text:
I'm required to submit
everything from plane tickets

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt50
label: ENFPc
text: to accommodation and taxi receipts,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt51
label: ENFPc
text:
to multiple witness statements
from each country.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt52
label: ENFPc
text:
I struggled to find
two people in each country

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt53
label: ENFPc
text: that spoke, read and wrote in English

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt54
label: ENFPc
text:
that would be willing
to help me with my witness statements.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt55
label: ENFPc
text:
I had to plead with immigration
officers at every border

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt56
label: ENFPc
text:
to please stamp my passport
with enough ink,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt57
label: ENFPc
text:
to be able to read the name and the date
on the passport stamp.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt58
label: ENFPc
text:
I am now in the process of submitting
nearly 10,000 pieces of evidence

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt59
label: ENFPc
text: in chronological order,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt60
label: ENFPc
text:
documenting how I entered
and exited each country,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt61
label: ENFPc
text:
along with a detailed itinerary
of what I did in each place.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt62
label: ENFPc
text:
Beyond this very overwhelming
amount of paperwork,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt63
label: ENFPc
text: somewhere along this journey,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt64
label: ENFPc
text:
I discovered that there was
more than one element of my comfort zone

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt65
label: ENFPc
text:
that I was going to have to get out of
to get to where I wanted to go.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt66
label: ENFPc
text:
I now believe that there is a correlation
between our comfort zone

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt67
label: ENFPc
text: and our mind, body and soul.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt68
label: ENFPc
text:
If you know that
you have fears in general,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt69
label: ENFPc
text:
knowing exactly where
those fears are stemming from

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt70
label: ENFPc
text: is the first step towards overcoming them.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt71
label: ENFPc
text:
I personally have a few
very distinct fears.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt72
label: ENFPc
text:
I am afraid of heights, which stems
from my physical comfort zone.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt73
label: ENFPc
text: I have - I had a fear of being alone,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt74
label: ENFPc
text:
which was completely
controlled by my mind.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt75
label: ENFPc
text:
And I also am terrified of regret,
which comes straight from my soul.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt76
label: ENFPc
text: The reason why so many people

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt77
label: ENFPc
text:
are unsuccessful at getting
out of their comfort zone

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt78
label: ENFPc
text:
is because our comfort zone
is not just one thing.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt79
label: ENFPc
text: It's three.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt80
label: ENFPc
text:
The first is obvious,
our physical comfort zone.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt81
label: ENFPc
text: Naturally, what we fear most is death.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt82
label: ENFPc
text:
We're evolutionarily wired to avoid
situations where we could get hurt.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt83
label: ENFPc
text:
And that's why every cell
in my body was screaming

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt84
label: ENFPc
text:
when I was standing on the edge
of a 750-foot drop in Switzerland.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt85
label: ENFPc
text: The opportunity came up to bungee jump

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt86
label: ENFPc
text:
off of the third highest
platform in the world,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt87
label: ENFPc
text:
and being someone that was
always too afraid to jump off of rocks

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt88
label: ENFPc
text: into the water at the river,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt89
label: ENFPc
text: this was by far my greatest fear,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt90
label: ENFPc
text: and the idea of facing it head-on

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt91
label: ENFPc
text:
excited me just as much
as it terrified me.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt92
label: ENFPc
text:
When they strapped in my ankles
and perched me on the edge,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt93
label: ENFPc
text: I was shaking.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt94
label: ENFPc
text: Three ...

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt95
label: ENFPc
text: Two ...

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt96
label: ENFPc
text: One ...

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt97
label: ENFPc
text: I plunged into seven and a half seconds

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt98
label: ENFPc
text:
of the most intense sensory overload
I had ever experienced.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt99
label: ENFPc
text: Complete terror turned into utter euphoria

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt100
label: ENFPc
text:
and resulted in one of the most
significant moments of my life.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt101
label: ENFPc
text:
In that moment, I realized that I was
capable of pushing my body's limits

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt102
label: ENFPc
text:
and that it's something
that's actually worth doing.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt103
label: ENFPc
text: I realized what was possible

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt104
label: ENFPc
text:
and became instantly hooked
on the rush of having new experiences.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt105
label: ENFPc
text:
Little did I know at the time
that facing my biggest fear

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt106
label: ENFPc
text:
was what would ultimately lead me to
travelling to every country in the world,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt107
label: ENFPc
text: and out of 196 countries,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt108
label: ENFPc
text:
I have only found myself
in real, physical danger one time.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt109
label: ENFPc
text:
I traveled to Yemen as a photographer
for a Norwegian author

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt110
label: ENFPc
text:
who was writing a book about
the least visited countries in the world.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt111
label: ENFPc
text: On our last night in the country,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt112
label: ENFPc
text:
I woke up to the sound of gunshots
outside of my hotel.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt113
label: ENFPc
text: I jumped out of bed and ran to the window

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt114
label: ENFPc
text:
to see that there were 50 or so men
congregated in the parking lot,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt115
label: ENFPc
text: yelling and pushing each other around,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt116
label: ENFPc
text: with six cars with flashing headlights

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt117
label: ENFPc
text: blocking the only exit.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt118
label: ENFPc
text: With no security in sight,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt119
label: ENFPc
text:
I grabbed my phone
to call my contact in the country,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt120
label: ENFPc
text: who didn't answer

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt121
label: ENFPc
text:
because this was happening
around 2:00 in the morning.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt122
label: ENFPc
text:
I could hear voices
outside of my hotel room

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt123
label: ENFPc
text:
even though I knew that we were
the only people staying in the hotel.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt124
label: ENFPc
text:
That was the first time I had ever heard
a fully automatic weapon discharged.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt125
label: ENFPc
text:
I literally ducked
and looked around the room

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt126
label: ENFPc
text:
realistically looking
for the best place to hide.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt127
label: ENFPc
text:
In that moment,
there was nothing I could do

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt128
label: ENFPc
text:
but sit with my fear
of potentially being kidnapped,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt129
label: ENFPc
text: until eventually, all the men disappeared,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt130
label: ENFPc
text:
and I could cry myself to sleep
after the adrenaline wore off.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt131
label: ENFPc
text:
The next morning, I called -
I talked to my contact in the country

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt132
label: ENFPc
text:
and asked him what had happened
the night before.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt133
label: ENFPc
text: He responded with,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt134
label: ENFPc
text: "Oh, that?

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt135
label: ENFPc
text: That was just a wedding party."

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt136
label: ENFPc
text: (Laughter)

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt137
label: ENFPc
text: Since Yemen is an Islamic country,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt138
label: ENFPc
text: they do not drink alcohol,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt139
label: ENFPc
text:
and one of the ways
that they celebrate is by shooting guns.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt140
label: ENFPc
text: Basically, what this means

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt141
label: ENFPc
text:
is the this scariest thing that
has ever happened to me while travelling

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt142
label: ENFPc
text:
was only scary because
I didn't fully understand the culture.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt143
label: ENFPc
text: The fun didn't stop there.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt144
label: ENFPc
text:
Getting out of the comfort zone
that I had created around myself mentally

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt145
label: ENFPc
text:
would prove to be
an even greater challenge

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt146
label: ENFPc
text: and would require me to develop

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt147
label: ENFPc
text:
an entirely different aspect
of my character.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt148
label: ENFPc
text: We are creatures of habit.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt149
label: ENFPc
text:
We are most comfortable with things
we can easily understand and predict.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt150
label: ENFPc
text: We fill our lives with routines.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt151
label: ENFPc
text: We wake up, go to class or work,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt152
label: ENFPc
text: eat our meals,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt153
label: ENFPc
text:
maybe work out and go to sleep
at basically the same times every day.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt154
label: ENFPc
text:
We surround ourselves with the same
stable relationships for years.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt155
label: ENFPc
text:
We try so hard to live up
to other people's expectations of us

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt156
label: ENFPc
text:
that sometimes we let our passions
take the back seat

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt157
label: ENFPc
text:
because ultimately we don't want
to become isolated from our society.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt158
label: ENFPc
text:
After I traveled to the first
hundred or so countries,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt159
label: ENFPc
text:
the destinations became
more and more obscure,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt160
label: ENFPc
text:
and I stopped being able to talk
my friends and family into coming with me.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt161
label: ENFPc
text:
If you've never traveled for an extended
period of time by yourself before,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt162
label: ENFPc
text:
it might be hard to imagine
what it's like to spend days in transit

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt163
label: ENFPc
text: on airplanes, in airports,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt164
label: ENFPc
text:
just to end up in an empty hotel room
by yourself at the end of the night.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt165
label: ENFPc
text: After months of this for me,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt166
label: ENFPc
text: it resulted in intense loneliness,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt167
label: ENFPc
text:
which was something
I didn't even realize I feared

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt168
label: ENFPc
text:
because I had been sheltered
from it my whole life.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt169
label: ENFPc
text: At the peak of my time spent alone,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt170
label: ENFPc
text:
I found myself in the tiny
island nation of Tuvalu,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt171
label: ENFPc
text:
in the south Pacific with a population
of only 11,000 people.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt172
label: ENFPc
text:
I spent four days
in the capital, Funafuti,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt173
label: ENFPc
text:
because that's how often
flights go in and out of the country.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt174
label: ENFPc
text: There was no Wi-Fi, no cell reception,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt175
label: ENFPc
text:
no connection to the outside world
whatsoever other than a small post office,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt176
label: ENFPc
text:
which happened to also be the country's
number one tourist attraction.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt177
label: ENFPc
text:
When I thought that I would be spending
my time in Tuvalu completely alone

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt178
label: ENFPc
text: and without any distraction,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt179
label: ENFPc
text:
I noticed the only
other foreigner on the island.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt180
label: ENFPc
text:
She was a kindergarten teacher
from the South Side of Chicago

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt181
label: ENFPc
text:
who also happened to be travelling
to every country.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt182
label: ENFPc
text:
We bonded so quickly and deeply
over all of our shared experiences

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt183
label: ENFPc
text:
that we ended up going
from complete strangers

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt184
label: ENFPc
text:
to travelling to Fiji, Tonga, Chad,
Central African Republic

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt185
label: ENFPc
text: and Saudi Arabia together.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt186
label: ENFPc
text: From the seven and a half months

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt187
label: ENFPc
text:
I spent travelling alone
to 50 or so countries,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt188
label: ENFPc
text:
I learned how to be alone
without being lonely,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt189
label: ENFPc
text:
and this did wonders
for my self-confidence,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt190
label: ENFPc
text:
but it also completely changed the way
that I think about the people in my life.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt191
label: ENFPc
text:
Now I have an appreciation
for the time that I get to spend

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt192
label: ENFPc
text:
with the people that I care about the most
in a way that I used to take for granted,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt193
label: ENFPc
text:
before I knew what it was
truly like to be alone.

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt194
label: ENFPc
text:
I also discovered that we have
so much more in common

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt195
label: ENFPc
text:
with people around the world
than you may think,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt196
label: ENFPc
text:
because ultimately
we all want the same things,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt197
label: ENFPc
text: which is why

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt198
label: ENFPc
text: at the root of our spiritual comfort zone,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt199
label: ENFPc
text: the layer closest to our souls,

id: ENFPc_Life Lessons from the Youngest Person to Travel to Every Country | Lexie Alford | TEDxKlagenfurt200
label: ENFPc
text: we are all looking for fulfillment.

text:
and there was this big box
in front of the Christmas tree,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries10
label: INFJ
text:
and I just dove in and opened it up,
and there was this big orange ball.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries11
label: INFJ
text: And he's been by my side ever since.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries12
label: INFJ
text:
When I walked down the street
or went to school,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries13
label: INFJ
text: I always had Mr. Wilson with me.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries14
label: INFJ
text:
And then I went on to college
and obviously played college basketball.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries15
label: INFJ
text:
Then I went on
to play professional basketball,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries16
label: INFJ
text:
and he's been actually a part of my life
in my business career.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries17
label: INFJ
text:
So we've been on this journey
for a long time,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries18
label: INFJ
text: and it's been an interesting journey.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries19
label: INFJ
text:
And one of the things
that we've been able to do

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries20
label: INFJ
text: is meet some amazing people.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries21
label: INFJ
text: Those amazing people are elite athletes;

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries22
label: INFJ
text:
not just your regular athletes
but your elite athletes.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries23
label: INFJ
text:
Now, a lot of you are going to say,
"I can't relate to these people.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries24
label: INFJ
text: "They're superhuman, these men and women."

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries25
label: INFJ
text:
I'll give you a little secret:
they're just like you and me.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries26
label: INFJ
text: I actually had a front row seat.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries27
label: INFJ
text:
OK, I was at the end of the bench,
watching, and observing, and learning

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries28
label: INFJ
text:
from these world-class 
amazing kind of athletes.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries29
label: INFJ
text:
But what I want to give you today
is a window into that world

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries30
label: INFJ
text:
that a lot of us
don't have an opportunity to.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries31
label: INFJ
text:
And a lot of us think
that these amazing athletes

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries32
label: INFJ
text: are there because of their talent,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries33
label: INFJ
text:
but Mr. Wilson and I realized
it's really not.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries34
label: INFJ
text: It's about a competitive mindset.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries35
label: INFJ
text:
They actually see, and think, and behave
so much different than we do.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries36
label: INFJ
text:
And that's what I want to share with you:
some two key points that we saw

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries37
label: INFJ
text:
that maybe you could use
in your daily life or in your business.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries38
label: INFJ
text:
The two points are visualization
and deliberate practice.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries39
label: INFJ
text: Let's start with visualization.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries40
label: INFJ
text:
A lot of us think that visualization
is about seeing a goal ahead of us.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries41
label: INFJ
text: But actually these people travel in time.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries42
label: INFJ
text:
They actually take 
their emotions, their senses

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries43
label: INFJ
text:
- seeing, hearing, touching -
and they go into the future.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries44
label: INFJ
text:
What they're doing is defining
their own reality, their own future,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries45
label: INFJ
text: and they're living there.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries46
label: INFJ
text: And then they come back,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries47
label: INFJ
text:
and then they have already
created an imprint,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries48
label: INFJ
text:
a blueprint of what success
is going to be for them.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries49
label: INFJ
text: Let me give you an example.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries50
label: INFJ
text:
I used to be a really good shooter,
and I used to shoot a lot of free throws.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries51
label: INFJ
text:
Before I shot a free throw,
I would actually--

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries52
label: INFJ
text:
- and you can take the time
if you want to follow with me -

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries53
label: INFJ
text:
is close your eyes, and I would think
about how I was holding the ball,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries54
label: INFJ
text:
I would think about the arc of the ball,
I would think of a really good backspin,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries55
label: INFJ
text: and it goes right through the net.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries56
label: INFJ
text: And what was really cool to me

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries57
label: INFJ
text:
if I could make the net 
flip up onto the rim.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries58
label: INFJ
text:
Then all I would do was open my eyes,
take a couple dribbles,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries59
label: INFJ
text: and I would just let it go.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries60
label: INFJ
text:
Nine out of ten times, 
I would make it, 90% of the time.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries61
label: INFJ
text:
What I didn't realize at that time
was with neuroscience today

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries62
label: INFJ
text:
when you actually visualize
what I was doing,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries63
label: INFJ
text:
you're actually using the same part
of the brain as if you were doing it.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries64
label: INFJ
text: And it's so powerful today.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries65
label: INFJ
text:
Even Jordan Spieth, 
the number-one golfer in the world,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries66
label: INFJ
text:
you've probably heard now with technology
their communication with him.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries67
label: INFJ
text:
Michael Geller would say
to Jordan Spieth, "Paint a picture."

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries68
label: INFJ
text:
Well, what he's saying is,
"Look at the flight of the ball.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries69
label: INFJ
text:
Watch it hit the green;
watch it roll onto the green.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries70
label: INFJ
text: How is it going to react?"

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries71
label: INFJ
text:
Jordan would say, "Got it," and he says,
"Make it happen," and so he does.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries72
label: INFJ
text:
One of the most powerful one 
of these visualizations

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries73
label: INFJ
text:
happened with a gentleman
named Colonel Nesmeth.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries74
label: INFJ
text:
He was an average golfer,
shot around 95.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries75
label: INFJ
text:
But something happened
in his life, tragically.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries76
label: INFJ
text:
He became a prisoner of war
during the Vietnam War.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries77
label: INFJ
text:
He was a prisoner 
for seven and a half years

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries78
label: INFJ
text: in a solitary confinement

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries79
label: INFJ
text:
of a cell no more 
than 5 feet by 5 feet by 5 feet.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries80
label: INFJ
text:
What would you do
if you were in that situation?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries81
label: INFJ
text: Well, he didn't want to give up hope.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries82
label: INFJ
text: He wanted to overcome this,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries83
label: INFJ
text: so what he did is he actually played golf.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries84
label: INFJ
text:
He didn't think about golf;
he was actually playing golf.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries85
label: INFJ
text: He visualized it.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries86
label: INFJ
text:
So what he would do for four hours
is play his golf course back home.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries87
label: INFJ
text: He would put a tee in the ground.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries88
label: INFJ
text:
He would hit it,
watch it go down the fairway,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries89
label: INFJ
text:
put the club back into the bag,
and start walking down the fairway.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries90
label: INFJ
text: He would hear the birds.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries91
label: INFJ
text: He would hear the clippers of the mowers.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries92
label: INFJ
text:
He would feel the wind on his back,
and he would keep on walking along.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries93
label: INFJ
text:
He would come up to his ball,
and he would repeat it again,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries94
label: INFJ
text: and he would feel the club in his hands.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries95
label: INFJ
text:
At the end of seven and half years,
he was finally released.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries96
label: INFJ
text: But he did this every day.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries97
label: INFJ
text:
Now remember I said 
that he had a shot around a 95.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries98
label: INFJ
text: That was his handicap, or his strokes.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries99
label: INFJ
text: What do you think he did when he came back

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries100
label: INFJ
text:
after not touching a club 
for seven and a half years?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries101
label: INFJ
text:
You would think he would at least
shoot a 95, but probably higher.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries102
label: INFJ
text: The amazing thing is, he shot a 75,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries103
label: INFJ
text: 20 strokes less than what he did,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries104
label: INFJ
text: by just doing visualization.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries105
label: INFJ
text:
This is a more powerful tool
that we can use in our daily lives.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries106
label: INFJ
text:
If you're a sales rep,
visualize your sales presentation.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries107
label: INFJ
text: If you're going to a job interview,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries108
label: INFJ
text:
visualize what's going to happen
in the job interview.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries109
label: INFJ
text: How many of you want to lose weight?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries110
label: INFJ
text: A lot of us want to lose weight.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries111
label: INFJ
text:
Visualize what you're going to look like
when you lose your weight.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries112
label: INFJ
text:
Put on the dress,
see yourself in the mirror.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries113
label: INFJ
text: eat the food that you need to do,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries114
label: INFJ
text:
because when you come back,
you've already created an imprint

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries115
label: INFJ
text:
of what success 
is going to look like for you.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries116
label: INFJ
text:
Jack Nicklaus had a saying,
"I never hit a shot, not even in practice,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries117
label: INFJ
text:
without having a very sharp
in-focus picture in my head."

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries118
label: INFJ
text:
The second thing I want to talk about is
we all want to be successful.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries119
label: INFJ
text:
But nothing cripples success
or performance than damaged confidence.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries120
label: INFJ
text:
So we see these athletes
as being super confident

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries121
label: INFJ
text: because of their talent, right?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries122
label: INFJ
text: But it's not.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries123
label: INFJ
text:
There was a study in the UK
that was extensive,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries124
label: INFJ
text:
and determined innate gifts
do not determine success.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries125
label: INFJ
text: So then what's going on?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries126
label: INFJ
text: It's hard work.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries127
label: INFJ
text:
No, it's not just hard work,
it's specific hard work.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries128
label: INFJ
text:
And that was discovered
by Anders Ericsson

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries129
label: INFJ
text: from Florida State University.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries130
label: INFJ
text:
And he did a groundbreaking study
determining about deliberate practice.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries131
label: INFJ
text:
What is deliberate practice
by Anders Ericsson?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries132
label: INFJ
text:
"It is the activities 
that are explicitly intended

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries133
label: INFJ
text: to improve performance

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries134
label: INFJ
text:
that reaches for objectives
just beyond one's level of competence."

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries135
label: INFJ
text:
There's four tenets that I want
to share with you today.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries136
label: INFJ
text:
One of the tenets is:
you have to make it personal,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries137
label: INFJ
text:
and you have to base it
upon principles of fundamentals.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries138
label: INFJ
text:
A lot of us would practice
shooting free throws

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries139
label: INFJ
text:
by getting on the free throw line
and doing it many, many times.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries140
label: INFJ
text: What deliberate practice is

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries141
label: INFJ
text:
is using something
in your fundamentals to build upon.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries142
label: INFJ
text:
So I would actually go to the front
of the rim and actually shoot straight up,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries143
label: INFJ
text:
because I knew arc was 
an important fundamental in shooting.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries144
label: INFJ
text:
Then it would come straight down
through the hole, or the hoop.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries145
label: INFJ
text:
Did you know that two basketballs
can fit through a hoop at the same time?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries146
label: INFJ
text: That's how big it is.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries147
label: INFJ
text:
So one of the tenets is
basically working on something

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries148
label: INFJ
text: of your fundamentals and strengths.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries149
label: INFJ
text:
Then the next is obviously repetition:
repetition, repetition, repetition.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries150
label: INFJ
text:
So I would do this for 50 times,
and then I would do it 100 times.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries151
label: INFJ
text:
But then I would add the third tenet,
which is stretch your abilities.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries152
label: INFJ
text: Get out of your comfort zone.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries153
label: INFJ
text:
So then what I would do
is then I would have to do it

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries154
label: INFJ
text: without the ball touching the rim.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries155
label: INFJ
text: Think about how hard that could be.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries156
label: INFJ
text:
That is what makes 
deliberate practice so difficult,

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries157
label: INFJ
text: because it's tedious and painful.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries158
label: INFJ
text:
But if you do it, you'll be successful
in what you want to accomplish.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries159
label: INFJ
text:
The fourth tenet is something
that we naturally should know

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries160
label: INFJ
text:
but we don't;
that is you need feedback.

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries161
label: INFJ
text:
How are you going to improve
without beginning the feedback?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries162
label: INFJ
text:
A lot of us do things on our own,
but guess what?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries163
label: INFJ
text: Don't these people have coaches?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries164
label: INFJ
text:
Don't they have people, advisers,
and people looking at them

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries165
label: INFJ
text: to give them the feedback that they need?

id: INFJ_Secrets of elite athletes | Kenn Dickinson | TEDxSnoIsleLibraries166
label: INFJ
text:
So, now after you've seen

it kind of makes sense
why they are so confident in what they do.

label: INFJ

label: INFJ

label: INFJ

That is the ability to create

determine it, live there

And then your choices

and you have to work on

The next step after that is basically,

And a lot of us know

label: INFJ
text:
And the third part is:
this is a journey for these people.

label: INFJ

Because they never stop;

It's about their way of ability
to measure or benchmark

label: ESTJc

label: ESTJc
text: through these techniques and applying it

id: ESTJc_Science of Thought | Caroline Leaf | TEDxOaksChristianSchool197
label: ESTJc
text: to this school and I saw change all over

id: ESTJc_Science of Thought | Caroline Leaf | TEDxOaksChristianSchool198
